    "For instance, the named phrase \"unable to move his hands, arms or legs.",
    "\", the model often erroneously segments this into \"unable to move his hands'' and \"arms or legs,\" revealing a shortcoming in its grasp of language understanding.",
    "In our next steps, we intend to improve rare entity extraction, such as social circumstances, by leveraging ontologies and terminologies in these specific domains.",
    "We also plan to enhance the embeddings within LLMs to broaden their coverage of these rare entities.",
    "Furthermore, expanding our dataset to include drug AEs is on our agenda."
